      "title_zh": "安全研究员分享利用 Claude 结合 Trail of Bits 检查清单进行 C/C++ 代码审计的技巧",
      "title_orig": "RT solst/ICE of Astarte: Re @trailofbits has markdown checklists for reviewing C and C++ codebases, and I’ve used those in conjunction with other Ski...",
